creator: KateMedia (Rentabox solutions)
descriptionHtml:
Our self-storage company in Vienna offers storage compartments for private customers as well as corporate customers in various storage sizes.

We offer optimal and air-conditioned storage conditions, as well as high safety and fire protection standards. The ceiling height of our storage room is 2.50 meters, but you only pay per square meter. So you can save the rent if you don't stack your boxes next to each other but on top of each other.

Our storage rooms are accessible all year round via an electronic access system.

Thats how it works:

Pick a location
Select your suitable storage room
Book the storage room


App functions:

Open the access door to the warehouse
Open your storage compartment
Track your bookings and the status history
